'''Charlie Dunbar Broad''' (* [[30. december]] [[1887]], [[Harlesden]] – † [[11. marec]] [[1971]], [[Cambridge (Cambridgeshire)|Cambridge]]) bol anglický [[filozof]], predstaviteľ [[neorealizmus|neorealistickej]] školy [[George Edward Moore|G. E. Moora]].

